\id 3JN Matupi Chin Standard Bible
\h 3 JOHAN
\toc1 3 JOHAN
\toc2 3Johan
\toc3 3Jn
\mt1 JOHAN CAPAT
\mt2 A Pathum Nah
\mt4 (John’s Third Letter)
\is2 JOHAN CAPAT (A PATHUMNAH) KAWNG
\im Tahae kah capat dongah he diklai pum la Pathen ol aka phong rhoek bomcen ham olpuei la a omnah kawng a thui. Olpuei la Khrihca bu khuikah a hamca la aka om Kaiyu taengah ca a tael pah. Anih long he Pathen olthangthen phong la aka cet rhoek muep a bom. Hekah ca he AD 85-95 tluk vaengah a tael.
\iot Sawt Yoeinah
\io1 Kuttuknah neh uemonah \ior (1-4)\ior*
\io1 Kodoknah neh huinah \ior (5-12)\ior*
\io1 Phihnah olrho\ior (13-15)\ior*
\c 1
\s1 Tuemnah Ol
\p 
